if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6aaad0c21c9611dc1c08d1f0546c467839f218d","tid":501902,"uid":134683,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"食啦契弟<br />\n分分鐘毒L幫N手埋單結婚結到專嚴都冇埋<br />\n你老味仲有心機擺上網<br />\n俾我就塞俾條八婆食然後拉大隊走啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d9f8f5f9853fb62f3aa332e72377b5576b0c17","tid":501902,"uid":80107,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"試問有邊個國家嘅男人會慘得過港男？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2698f8d1bb0eddcd855e1231159d1e84030ebc","tid":501902,"uid":19454,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T10:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留明見證一對新人離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本港離婚率高踞全球首五位 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5a351d68e603836a7681f268/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5a351d68e603836a7681f268%2F&d=rgQ2oB%2B6oMbIQfighRH3gkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=fffb9f0e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5a351d68e603836a7681f268/</a><br />\n<br />\n近十年本港離婚率持續上升，居於全球首五位之內。離婚對家庭帶來甚麼影響？<br />\n<br />\n這班中、小學生當中有些父母已離婚，有些父母很恩愛，有些關係時好時壞。他們對愛情、婚姻和離婚都有些看法。<br />\n<br />\n相愛容易相處難，有學者指出，夫婦在初婚、子女出生、子女入學以及退休時，最容易出現婚姻危機。因為踏入不同人生階段，夫妻會因角色轉變而情緒不穩，如果無處理感受，婚姻就很容易出現問題。<br />\n<br />\n近十年，香港的離婚數字不斷上升，離婚率大約百分之34，即每三對新人結婚，就有一對離異。去年已離婚男女逼近二十八萬人。"},{"pid":"71026da1df269d4afe7866459249c5a9854750c8","tid":501902,"uid":25794,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"埋單仲要俾人玩<br />\n傻鳩先結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922eee7a29277d3325ea59d01cabf13b93a61751","tid":501902,"uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma